{
  "texts": [
    "AI, artificial intelligence; GPS, Global Positioning System; ML, machine learning.",
    "Additional techniques for the anonymization of geo-referenced data (such as anonymized spatial coordinates and sample displacement) are being increasingly promoted 132.",
    "Many of these technologies can also be applied to livestock data, including new and improved methods of data acquisition and automated data analysis for determining livestock populations and characteristics such as species and breed.",
    "Two more livestock-specific innovations with substantial potential for providing data of great utility are animal-based methane measurement (in ruminants) and precision livestock farming.",
    "Several non-invasive methods are available to measure methane production in animals."
  ]
}